    nursingActions: ["Complete cultural and spiritual assessment on admission", "Use qualified medical interpreters, NOT family members, for important conversations", "Ask about specific after-death wishes before death occurs", "Facilitate visits from spiritual leaders as requested", "Accommodate dietary restrictions based on religious beliefs", "Allow space and time for prayer, meditation, or spiritual practices", "Respect modesty and gender preferences for care providers", "After death: follow cultural preferences for body preparation, viewing time, and rituals"],
